query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.favorite_count >= 0 AND q.favorite_count <= 10000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('applescript',
'html-parsing',
'iis-7.5',
'ip',
'overloading',
'reactive-programming',
'ruby-on-rails-3.1',
'shared-ptr',
'webrtc');
